description.en:
Nyantereum is a striving community token.

It distributes small amounts of their value to participants in the community, through Airdrops and more.

Continuously improvement of their own applications and more theme based design is a striving point for adoption & usage increasement.

We are available on Telegram, Twitter & Discord through implementation in one of the major providers.

Nyantereum is focused on creating a future proof and known currency for sending and receiving money in community's.

It will also be used as a store for value on Ethereum in its currency.

Currently aggregating large community interest and usage.

Future plans for further development are in discussion after we have successfully established a community with stronghold.

Fund’s then, will be used for application development & worldwide integration.
